en_129967_0	President Maithripala Sirisena made a request from the farmers in Polonnaruwa today, not to blame the government when they face a scarcity of water for cultivation.
en_129967_1	The President stated this while addressing the national ceremony of Aluth Sahal Mangalya held at Gal Vihara premises in Polonnaruwa today.
en_129967_2	The President also revealed that previously there were plans to supply water for the new season by 1st of April.
en_129967_3	However, as the farmers disagreed, the water will be supplied following the New Year festival.
